org.eclipse.viatra.dse.genetic.debug

Class BaseTestRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.genetic.debug.BaseTestRunner
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GeneticTestRunner

    public abstract class BaseTestRunner
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of this class can be used for running tests configured by a csv file (each row is a test case) and create the corresponding csv results file.

      • getResultsHeader

        public abstract java.lang.String getResultsHeader()
        Returns a string which will be the header of the results file. The string should contain one line with column names separated by commas. Note that there are a few predefined columns, see BaseTestRunner.BaseResult for details.
        Returns:
        Column names separated by semicolons.

        Runs the desired tests.
        Parameters:

        result - The base results, used to fill the attributes report and runTime.
